模块实现\\n\\n> ⚠️ 状态：部分实现（后端 API 与 Mobile 骨架已补齐，部分 UI 细节待 
Design-Only PR 后完善）\\n\\n## 职责\\n\\n负责推荐卡片生成、滑动操作处理、双向匹
配判定与通知。\\n\\n## 流程图\\n\\n### 推荐卡片\\n\\n```mermaid\\nsequenceDiagra
m\\n    participant C as Flutter App\\n    participant API as MatchingController
\\n    participant S as MatchingService\\n    participant DB as MySQL\\n    part
icipant R as Redis\\n\\n    C->>API: GET /matching/recommendations\\n    API->>S
: getRecommendations(userId, location, filters)\\n    S->>R: get candidate pool\
\n    alt cache miss\\n        S->>DB: query candidates (Haversine + filters)\\n
       DB-->>S: user list\\n        S->>R: cache candidate pool (TTL 5min)\\n   
end\\n    S-->>API: sorted cards\\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\\n```\\n\\n### 滑动与匹
配\\n\\n```mermaid\\nsequenceDiagram\\n    participant C as Flutter App\\n    pa
rticipant API as MatchingController\\n    participant S as MatchingService\\n   
participant DB as MySQL\\n    participant WS as Socket.io\\n\\n    C->>API: POST
/matching/actions (target_id, action=like)\\n    API->>S: recordAction(userId, t
argetId, action)\\n    S->>DB: insert match_actions\\n    S->>DB: checkMutualLik
e(targetId, userId)\\n    alt mutual like\\n        S->>DB: create match + conve
rsation\\n        S->>WS: emit match:created to both users\\n    end\\n    S-->>
API: result\\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\\n```\\n\\n## 关键文件\\n\\n| 文件 | 路径 | 
状态 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| Controller | `apps/api/src/modules/matching/
matching.controller.ts` | 已实现 |\\n| Service | `apps/api/src/modules/matching/
